What is the volunteer project?
it's to make available to collectors and fans a life long animation and movie collection.

What type of Collection do you have?
Anything that I ever had in my hand about animation or movies: 
-Posters
-Photos
-Programs : Book that you got when they had a premiere of a movie. Awards program when you go to the awards Show.
-Children books based on animation
-Comic Books
-Coloring books : That's not very attractive
-Lobby cards
-Photos 
-The original animation Artwork... starting on the 1920's
-Figurines

How long this volunteer project have been running?
Since the summer 2014

How can you get involve or Sponsor?
All they have to do it's to call and will give them information on what we are doing and we welcome them to come and do some volunteer work wich is cataloguing much of it.

How did you come up with that idea?
I wanted to know what I was gonna do with my collection after I died and as I am not gonna do much after I died so I better do something now and it's a good cause for the kidney  foundation.

